{"type":"message","id":"0a3c75d5","parentId":"d27815f7","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:34:52.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"报错信息就是这两行：\n\n```\nSearch completed but no final answer was produced.\n```\n\n没别的了，连错误码都没有。kimi 这搜索 API 返回了个寂寞，就告诉你\"搜完了但没结果\"，具体为啥失败屁都没说。\n\n可能是：\n- 网络抽风\n- kimi 服务端挂了\n- 查询被过滤了\n- 或者这功能今天就是个摆设\n\n反正工具层面没抛异常，是 kimi 自己没生成答案。挺傻逼的，至少给个错误原因吧？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":11722,"output":108,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11830,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772094888822}}
