{"type":"message","id":"a6ce3361","parentId":"9e6a5648","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:39:11.667Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"网页也 fetch 不了。那我用现有的 ddgs_search 先顶着，或者你手动装：\n\n**手动安装步骤：**\n\n```bash\n# 克隆仓库\ngit clone https://github.com/slinusc/web-search-mcp-server.git\ncd web-search-mcp-server\n\n# 用 uv 或 pip 安装\nuv pip install -e .\n# 或\npip install -e .\n\n# 然后配置到 claude_desktop_config.json 或 OpenClaw 的 MCP 配置里\n```\n\n**配置示例：**\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"web-search\": {\n      \"command\": \"python\",\n      \"args\": [\"-m\", \"web_search_mcp_server\"]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n要不你先试试这么装？或者我直接用现在能用的 `ddgs_search` 给你搜周星驰看看效果？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":14001,"output":183,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14184,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772095144844}}
