{"type":"message","id":"be00980c","parentId":"9a7e26c4","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:40:19.522Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.exec:11","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ŀ¼: D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\web-search-mcp-server\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                  \r\n----                -------------         ------ ----                                                                  \r\nd-----        2026/2/26     16:40                config                                                                \r\n-a----        2026/2/26     16:40            725 .gitignore                                                            \r\n-a----        2026/2/26     16:40            998 docker-compose.yml                                                    \r\n-a----        2026/2/26     16:40            443 Dockerfile                                                            \r\n-a----        2026/2/26     16:40           9719 README.md                                                             \r\n-a----        2026/2/26     16:40             73 requirements.txt                                                      \r\n-a----        2026/2/26     16:40          19512 server.py"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":262,"aggregated":"Ŀ¼: D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\web-search-mcp-server\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                  \r\n----                -------------         ------ ----                                                                  \r\nd-----        2026/2/26     16:40                config                                                                \r\n-a----        2026/2/26     16:40            725 .gitignore                                                            \r\n-a----        2026/2/26    