orn-0.41.0\r\n  Attempting uninstall: starlette\r\n    Found existing installation: starlette 0.52.1\r\n    Uninstalling starlette-0.52.1:\r\n      Successfully uninstalled starlette-0.52.1\r\n  Attempting uninstall: sse-starlette\r\n    Found existing installation: sse-starlette 3.2.0\r\n    Uninstalling sse-starlette-3.2.0:\r\n      Successfully uninstalled sse-starlette-3.2.0\r\n  Attempting uninstall: mcp\r\n    Found existing installation: mcp 1.26.0\r\n    Uninstalling mcp-1.26.0:\r\n      Successfully uninstalled mcp-1.26.0\r\n"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772095244999}}
