{"type":"message","id":"760b2179","parentId":"1d6ed855","timestamp":"2026-02-26T10:46:40.605Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_12440df2e9014fc5af3e4263","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"To install the `heventure-search-mcp` server, you can follow one of two main installation methods as provided in the documentation.\n\n### Method 1: Install via PyPI (Recommended)\n\n1. Use the following command to install:\n   ```bash\n   pip install heventure-search-mcp\n   ```\n\n2. After installation, you can run the server by executing:\n   ```bash\n   heventure-search-mcp\n   ```\n\n### Method 2: Install via `uvx`\n\n1. Install using `uvx` with the command:\n   ```bash\n   uvx heventure-search-mcp\n   ```\n\nThis straightforward procedure ensures that the `heventure-search-mcp` server is correctly installed and operational on your system. By following these steps, you can efficiently leverage the functionalities offered by the server for your MCP needs [1, 4].\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"gentle-orbit","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"To install the `heventure-search-mcp` server, you can follow one of two main installation methods as provided in the documentation.\n\n### Method 1: Install via PyPI (Recommended)\n\n1. Use the following command to install:\n   ```bash\n   pip install heventure-search-mcp\n   ```\n\n2. After installation, you can run the server by executing:\n   ```bash\n   heventure-search-mcp\n   ```\n\n### Method 2: Install via `uvx`\n\n1. Install using `uvx` with the command:\n   ```bash\n   uvx heventure-search-mcp\n   ```\n\nThis straightforward procedure ensures that the `heventure-search-mcp` server is correctly installed and operational on your system. By following these steps, you can efficiently leverage the functionalities offered by the server for your MCP needs [1, 4].\n","name":"mcporter call"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772102800601}}
