{"type":"message","id":"9cead878","parentId":"b639e0c6","timestamp":"2026-02-26T11:05:28.315Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bebc80707b134a5a8c1f17db","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"ddgs_search\": {\n      \"command\": \"python\",\n      \"args\": [\"D:\\\\gooddog\\\\scripts\\\\mcp_ddgs_server.py\"]\n    },\n    \"dashscope_websearch\": {\n      \"url\": \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/mcps/WebSearch/mcp\",\n      \"headers\": {\n        \"Authorization\": \"Bearer sk-8937a309c5f04f909aabd1ad255b3654\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"imports\": []\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772103928310}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac18694d","parentId":"9cead878","timestamp":"2026-02-26T11:05:33.364Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"配置里已经有正确的 key 了（sk-8937a309c5f04f909aabd1ad255b3654）。用户说设为\"默认 web 工具\"，但 mcporter 没有\"默认工具\"的概念，每次调用需要指定服务器名。\n\n不过我可以记在 TOOLS.md 里，方便以后直接用。让我更新 TOOLS.md。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置里已经有正确的 key 了。mcporter 没有\"默认工具\"的概念，每次调用得指定服务器名。\n\n我把它记到 TOOLS.md 里，以后直接用：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ea03b697b7244f8ca26e7346","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":78536,"output":261,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772103928316}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d60529f","parentId":"ac18694d","timestamp":"2026-02-26T11:05:33.375Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ea03b697b7244f8ca26e7346","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\n## MCP 搜索工具使用指南\n\n### 推荐：ddgs_search（多后端，国内更稳）\n\n**优先使用此工具**，走好狗那套多后端（auto + Bing 回退），网络不稳时更容易出结果。\n\n```bash\n# 基本搜索\nmcporter call ddgs_search.web_search query=\"你想搜的内容\"\n\n# 指定结果数（默认10，最大20）\nmcporter call ddgs_search.web_search query=\"关键词\" max_results=10\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- ✅ 多引擎自动切换（ddgs auto + Bing 回退）\n- ✅ 国内网络更稳定\n- ✅ 支持中英文搜索\n- ✅ 返回标题、URL、摘要\n\n---\n\n### 备用：ddgsearch.monica-search（AI 生成答案）\n\n当 ddgs_search 失败时，可用 Monica AI 搜索作为备用。\n\n```bash\nmcporter call ddgsearch.monica-search query=\"关键词\"\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- ✅ AI 生成综合答案\n- ✅ 带引用来源\n- ⚠️ 不如 ddgs_search 稳定\n\n---\n\n### 已弃用：ddgsearch.web-search / iask-search\n\n这两个工具在国内网络环境下经常超时/被墙，不推荐使用。\n\n```bash\n# ❌ 不推荐，容易失败\nmcporter call ddgsearch.web-search query=\"...\"\nmcporter call ddgsearch.iask-search query=\"...\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 其他工具\n\nSkills define _how_ tools work. This file is for _your_ specifics — the stuff that's unique to your setup.\n\n### Cameras\n\n- living-room → Main area, 180° wide angle\n- front-door → Entrance, motion-triggered\n\n### SSH\n\n- home-server → 192.168.1.100, user: admin\n\n### TTS\n\n- Preferred voice: \"Nova\" (warm, slightly British)\n- Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772103933370}}
{"type":"message","id":"58e7e960","parentId":"6d60529f","timestamp":"2026-02-26T11:05:56.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在更新 TOOLS.md，把 dashscope_websearch 设为首选推荐工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_148d4ee05c99449faae0b732","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","oldText":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\n## MCP 搜索工具使用指南\n\n### 推荐：ddgs_search（多后端，国内更稳）\n\n**优先使用此工具**，走好狗那套多后端（auto + Bing 回退），网络不稳时更容易出结果。\n\n```bash\n# 基本搜索\nmcporter call ddgs_search.web_search query=\"你想搜的内容\"\n\n# 指定结果数（默认 10，最大 20）\nmcporter call ddgs_search.web_search query=\"关键词\" max_results=10\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- ✅ 多引擎自动切换（ddgs auto + Bing 回退）\n- ✅ 国内网络更稳定\n- ✅ 支持中英文搜索\n- ✅ 返回标题、URL、摘要\n\n---\n\n### 备用：ddgsearch.monica-search（AI 生成答案）\n\n当 ddgs_search 失败时，可用 Monica AI 搜索作为备用。\n\n```bash\nmcporter call ddgsearch.monica-search query=\"关键词\"\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- ✅ AI 生成综合答案\n- ✅ 带引用来源\n- ⚠️ 不如 ddgs_search 稳定\n\n---\n\n### 已弃用：ddgsearch.web-search / iask-search\n\n这两个工具在国内网络环境下经常超时/被墙，不推荐使用。\n\n```bash\n# ❌ 不推荐，容易失败\nmcporter call ddgsearch.web-search query=\"...\"\nmcporter call ddgsearch.iask-search query=\"...\"\n```","newText":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\n## MCP 搜索工具使用指南\n\n### 首选：dashscope_websearch（阿里云百炼，国内最快最稳）\n\n**默认用这个！** API Key 已配置，直接调用。\n\n```bash\n# 基本搜索（默认 5 条结果）\nmcporter call dashscope_websearch.bailian_web_search query=\"你想搜的内容\"\n\n# 指定结果数（最大 10）\nmcporter call dashscope_websearch.bailian_web_search query=\"关键词\" count=10\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- ✅ 国内 API，速度快，不抽风\n- ✅ 返回标题、URL、摘要、站点 logo\n- ✅ 支持中英文搜索\n- ✅ 阿里云百炼官方服务，稳定可靠\n\n**API Key：** `sk-8937a309c5f04f909aabd1ad255b3654`（已配置在 mcporter.json）\n\n---\n\n### 备用：ddgs_search（本地 DuckDuckGo）\n\n当 dashscope 不可用时用这个。\n\n```bash\nmcporter call ddgs_search.web_search query=\"关键词\"\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- ✅ 本地运行，无需 API Key\n- ⚠️ 中文搜索偶尔跑偏，返回不相关内容\n\n---\n\n### 备用：ddgsearch.monica-search（AI 生成答案）\n\n需要 AI 总结时用这个。\n\n```bash\nmcporter call ddgsearch.monica-search query=\"关键词\"\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- ✅ AI 生成综合答案，带引用\n- ⚠️ 比原始搜索慢\n\n---\n\n### 已弃用/不推荐\n\n| 工具 | 问题 |\n|------|------|\n| `ddgsearch.web-search` | 经常 canceled，不稳定 |\n| `ddgsearch.iask-search` | 国内容易被墙 |\n| `kimi web_search` | 经常\"Search completed but no final answer\" |\n| `heventure-search-mcp` | 入口脚本有 bug，无法正常运行 |\n| `websearch` (slinusc) | 依赖 SearXNG，DuckDuckGo 在国内被墙 |"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":79161,"output":913,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80074,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772103933376}}
